      "updated": 1770058520992,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Django provides built in authentication out of the box. We will see how we can use that and how we can \noverrite existing User model.\n\nIn Django we have User Model that we can use for builtin authentication.",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 8,
